# Place your .glb 3D model files here

This folder is for storing your Unity-exported food models.

## Supported formats:
- .glb (binary glTF - recommended)
- .gltf (text glTF + separate textures)

## File naming:
- burger.glb
- pizza.glb
- cake.glb
- smoothie.glb
- etc.

## Upload your models:
1. Export from Unity as glTF 2.0
2. Upload .glb file here via GitHub web UI
3. Update ar-viewer.html to point to: 
   https://atv432.github.io/dine-ar/assets/models/your-model.glb
